578
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:33,120
<i>Mayday. Mayday. Mayday.</i>

579
00:34:33,200 --> 00:34:35,080
<i>This is the </i>Mariposa<i>. We are sinking.</i>

580
00:34:35,160 --> 00:34:38,040
<i>Last known position:
24 degrees, 33 north</i>

581
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:39,560
<i>and 74, 56 west.</i>

582
00:34:39,640 --> 00:34:40,760
