is what we came here for.

600
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:19,960
The Mosasaur is tagged.

601
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:21,760
We found it once,
we'll find it again.

602
00:35:21,840 --> 00:35:23,080
Maybe we can

