613
00:35:51,200 --> 00:35:54,240
24, 33 north, 74, 56 west.

614
00:35:55,080 --> 00:35:56,760
- Flank speed.
- Aye, aye.

615
00:35:57,680 --> 00:35:59,400
We're search and rescue now.

616
