It's my charter.

617
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:05,000
It's my boat.

618
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,800
Oh, my god.

619
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:42,400
Is that... is that...

620
00:36:42,480 --> 00:36:43,800
- Oh, my god. Hey.
- Oh, my god.

621
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:45,320
Hey! Hey!

622
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,720
- Hey, over here!
- Over here!

623
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:56,320
I don't know.
It was, like, the size of the boat.

624
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:59,160
Bigger. 50 feet, 70.
I... I don't know.

625
00:36:59,240 --> 00:37:02,240
It was a snakelike body
