729
00:42:47,520 --> 00:42:49,800
Yes! Come down ten knots!

730
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:52,720
Hard starboard. Down ten. Down ten.

731
00:42:56,640 --> 00:42:57,680
There it is!

732
00:42:57,760 --> 00:42:59,720
Port side off the stern rail.

733
00:43:02,760 --> 00:43:03,800
I got it!

734
00:43:03,880 --> 00:43:05,200
I got it!

735
00:43:14,920 --> 00:43:15,960
Nice shot.

736
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:17,960
Nice rocket.

737
00:43:19,040 --> 00:43:20,560
- That was fantastic.
- Yeah!

738
00:43:20,640 --> 00:43:22,160
That was genius.

739
00:43:22,240 --> 00:43:23,920
It worked, right?

740
00:43:24,920 --> 00:43:26,080
- Yes.
- That was good.

741
00:43:26,160 --> 00:43:27,760
It worked.

742
00:43:27,840 --> 00:43:29,200
Oh, god.

743
00:43:29,280 --> 00:43:34,000
You did it, you did it, right?
It worked, it worked.

744
00:43:34,080 --> 00:43:37,280
Oh, well done. Awesome, awesome.

745
00:43:37,360 --> 00:43:39,080
Kéké, did you see that?

746
00:43:40,520 --> 00:43:42,160
Gotta be calm. Just breathe.

747
00:43:42,240 --> 00:43:43,400
- Hey.
- Hey.

748
00:43:44,560 --> 00:43:45,760
What if we don't?

749
00:43:46,400 --> 00:43:47,440
What if we don't what?

750
