754
00:43:55,960 --> 00:43:58,200
Science is for all of us,
not some of us.

755
00:43:59,320 --> 00:44:00,520
Have you thought about that?

756
00:44:01,600 --> 00:44:02,800
No, I guess I haven't.

757
00:44:04,680 --> 00:44:06,160
Well, then maybe you should start.

758
00:44:07,720 --> 00:44:09,920
