- Dad, please.

759
00:44:10,640 --> 00:44:11,720
Hey, Xavier.

760
00:44:11,800 --> 00:44:13,320
Head between your legs,
deep breaths.

761
00:44:13,400 --> 00:44:15,480
Hey. Deep breaths. Deep breaths.

762
00:44:15,560 --> 00:44:17,800
Dad, I think I'm gonna be sick.

763
00:44:17,880 --> 00:44:19,240
It's all right. Just breathe.

764
00:44:28,680 --> 00:44:30,400
Those things from the boat.

765
