It's mutualism!

771
00:45:01,280 --> 00:45:03,360
Interspecies symbiosis!

772
00:45:04,320 --> 00:45:07,720
Those Spinosaurus,
they help the Mosasaur hunt.

773
00:45:08,400 --> 00:45:09,400
