Henry! Henry!

1313
01:33:17,320 --> 01:33:18,360
No!

1314
01:33:48,360 --> 01:33:49,360
Doc!

1315
01:33:49,640 --> 01:33:50,640
You okay?

1316
01:34:09,000 --> 01:34:10,120
Let's go home.

1317
01:35:17,440 --> 01:35:18,440
Isabella.

1318
01:35:19,280 --> 01:35:20,280
Honey.

1319
01:35:20,520 --> 01:35:21,520
Let's go.

1320
01:35:23,120 --> 01:35:24,200
We're almost there.

1321
01:35:51,360 --> 01:35:52,560
I see the helipad.

1322
01:35:53,440 --> 01:35:54,800
It's in the middle of a reservoir.

1323
01:35:56,880 --> 01:35:58,200
No sign of the kids, though.

1324
01:35:58,960 --> 01:36:00,600
Will they even be able
to find this place?

1325
01:36:01,560 --> 01:36:02,640
Hey.

1326
01:36:03,680 --> 01:36:05,080
Hey, there's footprints here.

1327
01:36:06,080 --> 01:36:07,080
Hello?

1328
01:36:07,760 --> 01:36:09,800
Reuben! Teresa!

1329
01:36:09,880 --> 01:36:11,536
Zora, they could be anything.
They could be animals.

1330
01:36:11,560 --> 01:36:12,880
- It could be...
- In Nikes?

1331
01:36:12,960 --> 01:36:14,736
Listen, I appreciate
what you're doing. I really do.

1332
01:36:14,760 --> 01:36:16,416
- But we are in a crunch right now.
- Hello?

1333
01:36:16,440 --> 01:36:18,056
And we don't even know
if they survived the rocks.

1334
01:36:18,080 --> 01:36:19,200
- Okay?
- Reuben! Teresa!

1335
01:36:19,280 --> 01:36:20,280
The helicopter's coming.

1336
01:36:20,360 --> 01:36:22,240
Well, we'll just have the pilots
do a low pass

1337
01:36:22,320 --> 01:36:23,656
over the whole island
while there's still light.

1338
01:36:23,680 --> 01:36:25,160
That is an incredibly dangerous idea.

1339
01:36:25,240 --> 01:36:26,480
Well, nobody asked you.

1340
01:36:27,480 --> 01:36:28,480
Hello?

1341
01:36:28,960 --> 01:36:30,160
Isabella!

1342
01:36:31,320 --> 01:36:32,360
Hello?

1343
01:36:33,320 --> 01:36:34,320
Hello?

1344
01:36:34,960 --> 01:36:36,240
Hello?

1345
01:36:37,880 --> 01:36:39,480
Anyone, please!

1346
01:36:41,760 --> 01:36:42,960
Hello?

1347
01:36:46,920 --> 01:36:47,960
Hello?

1348
01:36:48,360 --> 01:36:49,880
Is anyone here?

1349
01:36:51,160 --> 01:36:52,320
Hey!

1350
01:36:52,400 --> 01:36:54,800
- Oh, my god. You made it! Oh, god.
- Oh, my god!

1351
01:36:54,880 --> 01:36:56,040
- Oh, my god.
- Hi.

1352
01:36:56,120 --> 01:36:57,376
- You okay?
- Thank God you're alive.

1353
01:36:57,400 --> 01:36:59,640
Where is he? No... no.
Where is that son of a bitch?

1354
01:36:59,720 --> 01:37:01,280
- What? Who?
- That guy. The guy...

1355
01:37:01,360 --> 01:37:02,896
- He... he let me fall.
- Yeah, he tried to kill her.

1356
01:37:02,920 --> 01:37:04,080
Wait, wait. Who let you fall?

1357
01:37:07,040 --> 01:37:08,080
Hey, Krebs!

1358
01:37:11,360 --> 01:37:12,416
- I'm gonna kill him!
- Hey... hey, no.

1359
01:37:12,440 --> 01:37:13,520
He's got a gun, Teresa. No.

1360
01:37:14,520 --> 01:37:16,360
Hey, let's just settle down,
everybody, okay?

1361
01:37:18,520 --> 01:37:20,240
You stopped me calling for help!

1362
01:37:20,320 --> 01:37:21,760
You wanted me to die.

1363
01:37:21,840 --> 01:37:23,760
What are you talking about?
I tried to catch you.

1364
01:37:24,520 --> 01:37:27,280
No... no. You looked right at me,
and you let me fall!

1365
01:37:27,960 --> 01:37:29,000
She's lying.

1366
01:37:30,320 --> 01:37:31,616
If she's lying,
then why do you have a gun?

1367
01:37:31,640 --> 01:37:33,200
Because she's hysterical.

1368
01:37:34,240 --> 01:37:36,320
No, I'm not hysterical.
I'm homicidal!

1369
01:37:36,400 --> 01:37:38,080
- Hey, whoa... whoa.
- Hey... hey.

1370
01:37:38,160 --> 01:37:39,920
- Don't rush the guy with a gun.
- Enough.

1371
01:37:40,000 --> 01:37:41,160
All right.

1372
01:37:41,240 --> 01:37:42,240
All right.

1373
01:37:42,480 --> 01:37:44,000
Yes, everybody just relax.

1374
01:37:44,080 --> 01:37:45,320
Why don't I take that?

1375
01:37:46,400 --> 01:37:47,440
It looks heavy.

1376
01:37:51,800 --> 01:37:56,000
And... I'll keep it safe with me.

1377
01:37:58,440 --> 01:38:00,120
Now, we're all just gonna relax

1378
01:38:00,200 --> 01:38:02,400
and wait here
for the helicopter to arrive.

1379
01:38:03,800 --> 01:38:05,040
There's a helicopter coming?

1380
01:38:05,520 --> 01:38:07,440
Any minute.
We just got to make sure they see us.

1381
01:38:07,840 --> 01:38:08,960
Told you we'd made it.

1382
01:38:09,360 --> 01:38:10,720
Then we all get on the helicopter

1383
01:38:10,800 --> 01:38:13,960
and we forget any ridiculous stories
about whatever she said.

1384
01:38:14,040 --> 01:38:16,440
- I think we all need to...
- Stop talking! Stop talking.

1385
01:38:27,000 --> 01:38:28,040
It's the generator.

1386
01:38:29,240 --> 01:38:30,520
They must be on a timer.

1387
01:38:35,280 --> 01:38:36,840
The generator sounds angry.

1388
01:38:37,440 --> 01:38:39,800
Maybe this place is deserted
in the daytime.

1389
01:38:40,520 --> 01:38:42,080
But not so deserted at night?

1390
01:38:58,360 --> 01:38:59,440
It's okay, honey.

1391
01:39:00,000 --> 01:39:01,000
It's okay.

1392
01:39:16,480 --> 01:39:17,480
Oh, not that thing.

1393
01:39:24,080 --> 01:39:25,080
Run!

1394
01:39:26,960 --> 01:39:28,000
Split up!

1395
01:39:30,240 --> 01:39:31,720
Go. Go, go.

1396
01:39:37,280 --> 01:39:38,760
Reuben! Reuben!

1397
01:39:44,680 --> 01:39:46,200
Teresa, get the rack!

1398
01:39:52,040 --> 01:39:53,440
What are they?

1399
01:39:53,520 --> 01:39:55,360
I don't know,
but they're mutant as shit!

1400
01:39:56,160 --> 01:39:57,480
Come on, get to the back!

1401
01:40:34,000 --> 01:40:35,320
The hell is this place?

1402
01:40:35,920 --> 01:40:37,040
It's a lab.

1403
01:40:37,120 --> 01:40:39,240
Crossbreeding, mutations.

1404
01:40:39,800 --> 01:40:41,200
It's where it all happened.

1405
01:40:59,480 --> 01:41:00,560
You're missing it!

1406
01:41:00,880 --> 01:41:02,640
- Give me the gun!
- Get off me!

1407
01:41:18,160 --> 01:41:19,880
- Dolores.
- Bella.

1408
01:41:23,480 --> 01:41:25,480
- You found us.
- Bella.

1409
01:41:29,720 --> 01:41:31,840
<i>Yummy candy.
I'm gonna eat you all up.</i>

1410
01:41:35,760 --> 01:41:36,840
It's okay.

1411
01:41:37,560 --> 01:41:38,560
Bella!

1412
01:41:44,960 --> 01:41:45,960
Bella!

1413
01:41:51,080 --> 01:41:53,200
<i>Yummy candy.
I'm gonna eat you all up.</i>

1414
01:41:56,200 --> 01:41:57,880
<i>Yummy candy.</i>

1415
01:42:01,640 --> 01:42:03,400
<i>I'm gonna eat you all up.</i>

1416
01:42:40,160 --> 01:42:41,160
Come on.

1417
01:42:43,080 --> 01:42:44,120
Come on, come on.

1418
01:43:36,960 --> 01:43:39,000
That way. Go... go. Give me that.

1419
01:43:43,160 --> 01:43:44,960
Hey. There's a tunnel system.

1420
01:43:45,240 --> 01:43:46,600
It goes under the whole island.

1421
01:44:00,280 --> 01:44:02,440
The tunnel leads to the ocean.
There's a boat.

1422
01:44:07,840 --> 01:44:09,000
It's the helicopter.

1423
01:44:10,880 --> 01:44:13,080
I'll get the kids.
You get the pilot's attention.

1424
01:44:14,200 --> 01:44:15,360
Don't let them leave, Doc.

1425
01:44:16,040 --> 01:44:17,120
Don't let them leave!

1426
01:44:43,120 --> 01:44:45,280
- I can't see anyone.
- Okay.

1427
01:44:45,360 --> 01:44:47,760
We circle for two minutes,
then get the hell out.

1428
01:45:21,280 --> 01:45:22,440
<i>Caution. Pedestrian ahead.</i>

1429
01:45:30,400 --> 01:45:31,400
Shit.

1430
01:45:39,400 --> 01:45:40,600
Down the tunnel. Quick.

1431
01:45:40,680 --> 01:45:42,240
Go... go.

1432
01:45:42,880 --> 01:45:44,880
- That way, go.
- It's okay. It's okay, Bella.

1433
01:45:56,280 --> 01:45:57,320
Come on, come on, come on.

1434
01:45:57,360 --> 01:45:58,400
You okay?

1435
01:45:58,480 --> 01:45:59,640
Which way do we go?

1436
01:45:59,720 --> 01:46:00,720
To the left. Hurry!

1437
01:46:00,800 --> 01:46:02,680
- Come on. Go... go.
- I'm scared.

1438
01:46:17,680 --> 01:46:19,320
Okay, I'm gonna call it.

1439
01:46:20,360 --> 01:46:21,360
Let's head home.

1440
01:46:33,800 --> 01:46:37,040
Hey! Stop! Hey!

1441
01:46:37,120 --> 01:46:38,480
Down here!

1442
01:46:38,560 --> 01:46:39,960
Come back!

1443
01:46:58,640 --> 01:46:59,840
Wait!

1444
01:46:59,920 --> 01:47:02,120
There. Seven o'clock, low.

1445
01:47:02,200 --> 01:47:04,200
I see it! Combing left!

1446
01:47:11,320 --> 01:47:12,600
Oh, thank God.

1447
01:47:12,840 --> 01:47:13,960
Come on.

1448
01:47:17,920 --> 01:47:19,000
Duncan!

1449
01:47:19,880 --> 01:47:21,240
They're coming back!

1450
01:47:37,920 --> 01:47:39,120
Hey!

1451
01:47:39,200 --> 01:47:41,320
Quick! Down here!

1452
01:48:00,280 --> 01:48:01,520
Loomis!

1453
01:48:02,080 --> 01:48:03,840
Kincaid, is that you?

1454
01:48:04,240 --> 01:48:05,720
- Reuben!
- Hello?

1455
01:48:05,800 --> 01:48:07,400
- Where are you guys?
- Hey!

1456
01:48:07,480 --> 01:48:08,880
- Down here! Hey!
- Here!

1457
01:48:08,960 --> 01:48:10,000
- Hey!
- Hey!

1458
01:48:10,080 --> 01:48:11,080
Oh, thank God.

1459
01:48:13,440 --> 01:48:14,920
- Get us out of here.
- Wait... wait.

1460
01:48:15,000 --> 01:48:16,840
Just wait... wait.

1461
01:48:19,120 --> 01:48:20,840
Did you... did you see that thing?

1462
01:48:21,320 --> 01:48:22,720
Get inside. Get inside.

1463
01:48:25,240 --> 01:48:26,640
Okay, listen up.

1464
01:48:27,120 --> 01:48:28,400
This is a drainage tunnel.

1465
01:48:28,960 --> 01:48:30,160
Leads down to the sea.

1466
01:48:30,240 --> 01:48:32,960
There's a... a dock
with a boat hanging on it. I saw it.

1467
01:48:33,040 --> 01:48:34,720
What about the helicopter?

1468
01:48:34,800 --> 01:48:37,200
- No helicopter.
- What?

1469
01:48:37,720 --> 01:48:38,720
- No.
- Wait.

1470
01:48:38,800 --> 01:48:41,080
- But what if the boat doesn't work?
- Hey.

1471
01:48:41,640 --> 01:48:43,400
I'm not gonna let you get hurt, okay?

1472
01:48:46,760 --> 01:48:48,080
All right. Come on.

1473
01:48:49,560 --> 01:48:51,440
This way. Let's get to the dock.

1474
01:49:01,760 --> 01:49:03,440
- Shut up!
<i>- Caution.</i>

1475
01:49:03,520 --> 01:49:05,000
<i>Pedestrian ahead.</i>

1476
01:49:29,800 --> 01:49:31,000
Down the tunnel. Quick.

1477
01:49:31,080 --> 01:49:32,616
I don't think
this is the right way, Dad.

1478
01:49:32,640 --> 01:49:34,160
Yeah, yeah. Come on. Go, go.

1479
01:49:36,960 --> 01:49:38,040
Zora!

1480
01:49:47,000 --> 01:49:48,000
Go!

1481
01:49:48,920 --> 01:49:50,880
- Are you okay?
- Go, go.

1482
01:49:51,880 --> 01:49:53,040
Krebs took the jeep.

1483
01:49:53,120 --> 01:49:55,280
If he gets to the boat before us,
he'll take that, too.

1484
01:49:55,760 --> 01:49:57,000
Come on, Z, we got to go.

1485
01:50:02,920 --> 01:50:04,880
There's the ocean! Up there!

1486
01:50:07,760 --> 01:50:10,176
- Hey, I see the boat. It's that way.
- How do we open the gate?

1487
01:50:10,200 --> 01:50:12,080
It's there. It's there.
The control panel.

1488
01:50:12,160 --> 01:50:13,520
I'll go. I'll go.

1489
01:50:14,440 --> 01:50:15,680
Can you fit through?

1490
01:50:15,760 --> 01:50:16,960
I'm trying! I'm trying!

1491
01:50:18,400 --> 01:50:19,640
Shit.

1492
01:50:23,560 --> 01:50:24,840
Maybe we can lift it.

1493
01:50:30,400 --> 01:50:32,360
Guys? That thing is back!

1494
01:50:32,440 --> 01:50:34,080
Again! All together, lift!

1495
01:50:34,160 --> 01:50:35,880
- One, two, three!
- Come on.

1496
01:50:41,680 --> 01:50:42,680
Hey.

1497
01:50:42,760 --> 01:50:43,920
- Hey... hey. Isabella.
- Hey!

1498
01:50:44,000 --> 01:50:45,760
- No... no. No, no!
- Bella! Bella, wait!

1499
01:50:45,840 --> 01:50:47,600
- Bella!
- Come back here! Come here!

1500
01:50:48,160 --> 01:50:49,880
- Careful, Bella. Be careful.
- Isabella!

1501
01:50:49,960 --> 01:50:51,080
Find the power button!

1502
01:51:10,320 --> 01:51:12,680
Hurry! We have to open the gate!

1503
01:51:12,760 --> 01:51:14,120
It's coming! It's coming!

1504
01:51:14,200 --> 01:51:15,520
- Hey!
- Hey!

1505
01:51:15,600 --> 01:51:18,080
Hey! Bella! Open the gate!

1506
01:51:40,000 --> 01:51:41,520
<i>Excess speed. Slow down.</i>

1507
01:51:44,800 --> 01:51:45,840
<i>Caution. Pedestrian ahead.</i>

1508
01:51:53,880 --> 01:51:54,880
Go... go.

1509
01:51:57,920 --> 01:51:59,680
We got to go. We got to go.

1510
01:51:59,760 --> 01:52:00,880
- Teresa, come on!
- Come on.

1511
01:52:06,000 --> 01:52:07,240
Now, Z, now!

1512
01:52:41,720 --> 01:52:42,720
Hurry.

1513
01:52:43,520 --> 01:52:44,920
The hoist control's over there. Go.

1514
01:52:45,600 --> 01:52:46,840
How do you get the boat down?

1515
01:52:48,280 --> 01:52:49,320
Lower the boat.

1516
01:52:50,000 --> 01:52:51,000
But where's the power?

1517
01:52:51,080 --> 01:52:52,256
- Here, take this!
- I got it. I got it.

1518
01:52:52,280 --> 01:52:53,360
Turn it on.

1519
01:52:53,440 --> 01:52:54,840
The hoist is broken.

1520
01:52:54,920 --> 01:52:56,240
It's jammed!

1521
01:52:56,320 --> 01:52:57,400
Come on, come on!

1522
01:53:08,920 --> 01:53:09,920
Bella!

1523
01:53:10,560 --> 01:53:11,800
Don't move, honey.

1524
01:53:18,720 --> 01:53:19,800
It's attracted to light!

1525
01:53:19,880 --> 01:53:21,760
Turn it off! Turn it off!

1526
01:53:22,080 --> 01:53:23,200
Give me the flares!

1527
01:53:23,280 --> 01:53:24,576
- What the hell are you doing?
- I got it.

1528
01:53:24,600 --> 01:53:25,680
- I got it. Go!
- No... no!

1529
01:53:25,760 --> 01:53:27,200
- What the hell are you doing?
- Hey!

1530
01:53:27,720 --> 01:53:29,080
Right here!

1531
01:53:29,720 --> 01:53:30,800
You want me?

1532
01:53:31,240 --> 01:53:32,240
Come on!

1533
01:53:32,800 --> 01:53:34,960
- Come on!
- No.

1534
01:53:35,400 --> 01:53:36,640
Duncan.

1535
01:53:36,720 --> 01:53:38,280
This way! Hey!

1536
01:53:38,360 --> 01:53:39,840
Get your sister! Get your sister!

1537
01:53:40,680 --> 01:53:41,960
Get out of here! Go!

1538
01:53:44,160 --> 01:53:46,120
Come here! This way!

1539
01:53:46,960 --> 01:53:48,440
- Come on!
- Duncan!

1540
01:53:49,080 --> 01:53:50,560
- Duncan!
- Hey!

1541
01:53:51,040 --> 01:53:52,040
Come on.

1542
01:53:53,680 --> 01:53:54,800
Don't wait, Zora!

1543
01:53:54,880 --> 01:53:56,960
Get the kids! Go!

1544
01:53:57,040 --> 01:53:58,840
- Come on!
- Save them.

1545
01:54:16,720 --> 01:54:17,800
Come on!

1546
01:54:18,960 --> 01:54:19,960
Shit.

1547
01:54:44,200 --> 01:54:45,320
Come on!

1548
01:54:47,760 --> 01:54:48,800
Yeah.

1549
01:55:01,480 --> 01:55:03,040
Go. Get in the boat. Get in the boat.

1550
01:55:03,120 --> 01:55:05,600
- Take the helm. Take the helm.
- Grab her, grab her, grab her.

1551
01:55:06,320 --> 01:55:07,760
Come on. There's no power.

1552
01:55:07,840 --> 01:55:09,280
- Check the power!
- Zora!

1553
01:55:10,400 --> 01:55:11,400
Duncan!

1554
01:55:11,840 --> 01:55:13,160
- Duncan!
- Zora, come on.

1555
01:55:13,640 --> 01:55:14,640
Duncan!

1556
01:55:16,000 --> 01:55:18,160
- We have to go. Come on.
- Hey...

1557
01:55:18,240 --> 01:55:20,640
- Dad, hurry!
- Go. Come on!

1558
01:55:20,720 --> 01:55:22,800
- Dad, hurry!
- I'm trying!

1559
01:55:22,880 --> 01:55:24,560
- I'm trying!
- Go... go!

1560
01:55:24,640 --> 01:55:26,440
- Hurry!
- I'm trying!

1561
01:55:29,400 --> 01:55:31,400
- Hurry!
- Reuben!

1562
01:55:31,480 --> 01:55:32,720
Come on, please!

1563
01:55:32,800 --> 01:55:35,200
- Hurry!
- Go! Go, push it!

1564
01:55:55,240 --> 01:55:56,440
Kincaid!

1565
01:55:58,440 --> 01:55:59,600
Duncan!

1566
01:56:24,520 --> 01:56:25,520
Dad.

1567
01:56:26,240 --> 01:56:27,400
Hey! Hey!

1568
01:56:32,040 --> 01:56:33,200
Turn the boat around!

1569
01:56:45,160 --> 01:56:46,200
There he is. I see him.

1570
01:56:46,560 --> 01:56:47,560
There!

1571
01:56:47,920 --> 01:56:49,400
Yeah, there! Go!

1572
01:56:50,200 --> 01:56:51,240
Hey!

1573
01:57:56,760 --> 01:57:57,760
Who do we give it to?

1574
01:58:05,720 --> 01:58:06,800
You decide.

1575
01:58:11,840 --> 01:58:12,920
